name: | Fall In Tehran |
description: | A hair strand over here, a couple over there. A bunch of doors closed up; behind them many sets of eyes wide open. Pools of sorrow drifting through the city as you walk its streets smiling, dreaming about a better tomorrow, every crosswalk is a battlefield, every goddamn bridge is a deathtrap, still you move past them all just to get a whiff of your misleading reality and feel proud about the emptiness you possess just by breathing and being alive. –"Beauty is all I seek; presence is all I can provide."- A whisper was heard within the boy's ears as he walked past a shadow. |
